data.description: Huge, Gorgeous Condominium in a Private, Charming Gated Community by the San Antonio Medical Center. Major Convenience Location! You can easily get to just about anywhere around the city, The Medical Center, UTSA, USAA, Downtown, tons of shopping, automotive services, about 10 minutes to SAT Airport, etc with easy access to Interstate 10 and Loop I-410. There is a giant Living Room, a spacious Dining Room, 3 large Bedrooms and more! The Master Suite is Huge. It features it's own Master Bathroom, a huge separate Vanity area and multiple closets! The Master Bedroom alone is about 300 square feet, not including additional rooms and ensemble.  The owner also recently added Granite Counters, Stainless Steel Appliances (including Bosch Double Ovens) and some new electrical plugs. The separate Dining Room continues with a large Wet Bar. Even more convenient, you also have your own Washer/Dryer with your unit. Your Covered Balcony even provides a short-cut to your own 2 covered Parking Spaces. The Community Swimming Pool Complex is very inviting, with a Clubhouse available for events. The grand spaciousness, charm, tranquility and ultra-convenient location are only a few reasons to go see this condo home as soon as possible!
